I"	<h3 id="find">find</h3>

<ul>
  <li>由物件的id，也就是主鍵（primary key）來尋找物件</li>
</ul>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="n">client</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Client</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">find</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="c1">#&lt;Client id: 10, first_name: "Ryan"&gt;</span>

<span class="vi">@item</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Items</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">find</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">params</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="ss">:id</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="c1">#</span></code></pre></figure>

<ul>
  <li>但我想要找多個id呢？放上陣列吧</li>
</ul>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="n">client</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Client</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">find</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="o">=&gt;</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="c1">#&lt;Client id: 1, first_name: "Lifo"&gt;, #&lt;Client id: 10, first_name: "Ryan"&gt;]</span></code></pre></figure>

<blockquote>
  <p>若不是find找不動物鍵，就會拋出 ActiveRecord::RecordNotFound 異常。</p>
</blockquote>

<h3 id="take">take</h3>

<ul>
  <li>取出幾筆資料，所以後面可以放參數決定找幾筆，不做排序</li>
</ul>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"><span class="n">client</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="no">Client</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">take</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># =&gt; [</span>
  <span class="c1">#&lt;Client id: 1, first_name: "Lifo"&gt;,</span>
  <span class="c1">#&lt;Client id: 2, first_name: "Sara"&gt;</span>
<span class="p">]</span></code></pre></figure>

<h3 id="find_by">find_by</h3>

<ul>
  <li>找出第一筆符合條件的資料</li>
</ul>

